Putting It Together – A Full Pipeline


View source
gapminder |&gt;
  filter(year == 2007) |&gt;
  mutate(gdp_billions = (pop * gdpPercap) / 1e9) |&gt;
  group_by(continent) |&gt;
  summarise(
    mean_lifeExp = round(mean(lifeExp), 1),
    total_gdp_bn = round(sum(gdp_billions), 0),
    n_countries = n(),
    .groups = "drop"
  ) |&gt;
  arrange(desc(mean_lifeExp))


# A tibble: 5 × 4
  continent mean_lifeExp total_gdp_bn n_countries
